headline: PayPal plans to make its stablecoin available on the Stellar network
summary: PayPal (PYPL) announced plans to make the PayPal USD stablecoin available on the Stellar network pending regulatory approval by the New York State Department of Financial Services, or NYDFS. Stellar is a blockchain designed for fast, low-cost payments and real-world utility.
